question: On which riverbanks is the center of Uppsala, Sweden located?
true_answer: The center is located on both banks of the Fyris River (Fyrisån)
asked_question_translated: Millise jõe kaldal asub Uppsala keskus Rootsis?
answer: Uppsala keskus Rootsis asub Fyrisåni jõe kaldal.
answer_translated_eng: The centre of Uppsala in Sweden is on the banks of the Fyrisån River.
